  <brief_title>The Effects of Resistance Training and Protein Supplementation in Healthy Elderly Men and Women.</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Resistance Type Exercise Training and Protein Supplementation on Skeletal Muscle Mass, Strength, and Muscle Characteristics in Healthy Elderly Men and Women</official_title>
